title: Nisreen Tafesh is enjoying her breakfast and the sunny weather... and this is what she said - Archyde
text: 2024-01-13 20:09:07 Saturday, January 13, 2024 10:09 pm Mirna Walid – Beirut – Syrian artist Nisreen Tafesh shared with the public a group of photos, in which she appeared to be enjoying her breakfast and the sunny weather. Nisreen Tafesh commented on the post, saying: “Important affirmations to start your day from Louise Hay. Read them with the eyes of your heart and feel their presence: Life supports me in all possible ways. Listen with love to the messages of my body.” Nisreen Tafesh had revealed her contract to star in the series “For Free”, as she published a group of photos during her contract for the series on her page on the social networking site and wrote, commenting: “Wait for me in the blessed month of Ramadan in the series (For Free),” and she continued, revealing the team. The work among them is that it is directed by Gamal Abdel Hamid, written by Hossam Moussa, and under the general supervision of Ahmed Gaber, “with a group of Egyptian stars: Hani Ramzy – Dalia El-Behairy – Wafa Amer – Khaled Selim – Amr Abdel Jalil.” These were the details of the news: Nisreen Tafesh is enjoying her breakfast and the sunny weather.. and this is what she said for today.
